
Release Notes
=============

0.1.13 (10-14-2019)

* Always use type flag with cmds.file when saving

0.1.12 (10-10-2019)

* Add ConstructMenu class to hold a ref to QMenu

    * Prevents QMenu from being garbage collected
    * Fixes crash issue that was plaguing maya

* Add flatten_references task to Publish Action

0.1.9 (06-14-2018)

* Push context to environment variables on scene changed
* Initialize resources in userSetup
* Revise create reference dialog
* Revise save changes dialog
* Remove kBeforeCreateReference callback
